task.summary: Deleted the UnitTest project and fixed some UI bugs identified by Aaron and aligned some other program sequences in correct order.
Finished up new requirements (#703, #737, #333), Refined requirements (#691, #693) to allow Live testing by Scott and Dan.

Implemented additional support to the Spanning Tree Protocol on the software level. This is in the form of a service that runs in the background continuously and forces a new connection to the strongest Endpoint signal level in real-time depending on the distance relative to the nearest endpoint.
Minor changes to the BinMoveService to include the new Export endpoint in the BroadcastReceiver accepted params
